name: Department Of Government Efficiency
description: Department of Government Efficiency, a movement ignited by the Dogefather, uniting all Doge lovers under one grand flag: D.O.G.E The tagline D.O.G.E, representing the Department of Government Efficiency, gaining traction due to its association with Donald Trump as he prepares for the upcoming US elections. This concept has been notably supported by Elon Musk, who has expressed his backing for Trump and is rumoured to be considered for a significant role within this proposed department if Trump secures office again. The D.O.G.E acronym caught the public’s attention when Elon Musk, the legend behind Dogecoin’s rise to the top of the memecoin world, used the phrase « Department of Government Efficiency (D.O.G.E). » Who could have predicted that this simple acronym would give birth to what might become one of the most iconic memes in existence?
